INGREDIENTS
Ice Bowls
* Two bowls, one smaller than the other
* Sliced citrus fruits
* Fresh mint
Ice Cream in a Bag
* 600ml double cream
* 1 tsp vanilla essence
* 1 tbsp sprinkles
* Half a bag of ice
* 1/2 cup rock ice
Peaches & Cream Lollies
* 2 cans of peaches
* 200ml cream
* Medium ziplock bags
Frozen Banana Ice Cream
* 4 bananas, cut into chunks and frozen
* Plant based milk
Frozen Watermelon Pops
* 1 large watermelon
* Melted chocolate
* Dessicated coconut

Fresh basil

node.text:
Cheese Stuffed Chicken Parmesan Meatballs
INGREDIENTS
500g chicken mince 
1 egg beaten
½ cup fresh breadcrumbs
½ cup finely grated parmesan cheese
2 tbsp chopped parsley 
2 cloves garlic, minced
Salt and pepper
 
Sliced ham
Cubed swiss cheese
 
2 tsp oil
40g butter
2 cloves garlic, minced
40g plain flour
2 cups chicken stock
1 cup heavy cream
1 tsp dijon mustard
400g penne pasta, cooked
1 cup grated cheddar cheese, divided
1 cup grated swiss cheese, divided
1 cup grated mozzarella, divided
Salt and pepper to taste
¼ cup pasta water 
 
Chopped parsley

INGREDIENTS
* 	2 sirloin steaks, sliced as thin as possible
* 	1 cup cream
* 	1 glass white wine
* 	1 cup beef stock
* 	2 cloves garlic, crushed
* 	1 small onion, finely chopped
* 	2 tsp oil
* 	2 tbsp parsley, finely chopped
* 	lots of chips
* 	salt and pepper, to taste
* 	2 tbsp plain flour
* 	3 tbsp butter
* 	1 tbsp black pepper, freshly ground
* 	1 cup parmesan, grated

node.text:
This Giant Crispy Chicken Cordon Bleu is no joke!

INGREDIENTS
* 	10 chicken breasts
* 	Salt & pepper
* 	20 x Emmental slices
* 	20x slices thin ham
* 	100g seasoned plain flour
* 	6 eggs, beaten with a little water and salt
* 	300g fine panko breadcrumbs
* 	100ml vegetable oil
* 	50g butter
* 	50g plain flour
* 	500g whole milk
* 	200g grated emmental

node.text:
We LOVE a samosa here at @twisted but we know that not everyone has the time to create a dough from scratch - so here are 4 fusion twists on the classic, introudcing traditonal - and VERY untraditonal flavours! Give them a go!

INGREDIENTS
Buffalo Chicken 
Butter 65g
Hot water 0.9 cups
Flour 2 cups
Salt, big pinch
Handful of chives, finely chopped
1 chicken breast, shredded
½ cup hot sauce 
½ cup Butter, melted
1 tsp Garlic powder 
Blue cheese ranch, to serve
 
Sausage Marinara 
3 Pork sausages
½ Onion, diced
3 Garlic cloves, minced
1 tbsp tomato paste
400g tinned tomatoes
½ tsp Oregano 
½ tsp sugar
Splash of balsamic vinegar
Salt and pepper to taste
White bread, 8 slices
Pesto, to serve
 
Crunch-wrap 
500g Ground beef 
1 Onion, diced
2 tsp taco seasoning
Diced tomatoes, onion, and coriander 
Sour cream
Queso 
Tortilla chips 
3 tortillas, halved
Chipotle crema, to serve
 
Butter chicken 
3 Chicken thighs, diced
1 tbsp Butter
1 onion, diced
3 Garlic, minced
1 tbsp Ginger paste 
1 tbsp Tomato paste
400g Chopped tomatoes
2 tbsp Honey 
½ cup Single cream
1 tsp Garam masala 
1 tsp turmeric
1 tsp Cumin 
½ tsp Coriander
3 Roti, halved
Green chutney, to serve

Chicken Parm Mac 'n' Cheese!

2 chicken breasts
150g plain flour
1 tsp dried Italian seasoning
2 eggs, whisked

140g panko breadcrumbs 
30g grated parmesan cheese
Oil for shallow frying

30g butter
30g flour
500ml milk
½ tsp mustard powder
¼ tsp paprika
tsp nutmeg
Salt and pepper to taste
400g cooked macaroni
100g grated mozzarella,
100g grated cheddar
50g grated gruyere

250g tomato pasta sauce 
50g grated mozzarella cheese
Fresh basil leaves

node.text:
Cheese Stuffed Chicken Parmesan Meatballs
INGREDIENTS
500g chicken mince 
1 egg beaten
½ cup fresh breadcrumbs
½ cup finely grated parmesan cheese
2 tbsp chopped parsley 
2 cloves garlic, minced
Salt and pepper
 
Sliced ham
Cubed swiss cheese
 
2 tsp oil
40g butter
2 cloves garlic, minced
40g plain flour
2 cups chicken stock
1 cup heavy cream
1 tsp dijon mustard
400g penne pasta, cooked
1 cup grated cheddar cheese, divided
1 cup grated swiss cheese, divided
1 cup grated mozzarella, divided
Salt and pepper to taste
¼ cup pasta water 
 
Chopped parsley

node.text:
INGREDIENTS
* 	2 sirloin steaks, sliced as thin as possible
* 	1 cup cream
* 	1 glass white wine
* 	1 cup beef stock
* 	2 cloves garlic, crushed
* 	1 small onion, finely chopped
* 	2 tsp oil
* 	2 tbsp parsley, finely chopped
* 	lots of chips
* 	salt and pepper, to taste
* 	2 tbsp plain flour
* 	3 tbsp butter
* 	1 tbsp black pepper, freshly ground
* 	1 cup parmesan, grated

#staplerecipes #mealprep #foodprep #chefmode #winnerwinnerchickendinner #pantryorganization #recipeshare #chickenfordinner #easyrecipes #noleftovers

This Giant Crispy Chicken Cordon Bleu is no joke!

INGREDIENTS
* 	10 chicken breasts
* 	Salt & pepper
* 	20 x Emmental slices
* 	20x slices thin ham
* 	100g seasoned plain flour
* 	6 eggs, beaten with a little water and salt
* 	300g fine panko breadcrumbs
* 	100ml vegetable oil
* 	50g butter
* 	50g plain flour
* 	500g whole milk
* 	200g grated emmental
* 	1 tbsp dijon mustard
